The bailiff smiled and said: âYes, sir.â

At tea the same evening Levin said to his brother:

âI fancy the fine weather will last. Tomorrow I shall start mowing.â

âIâm so fond of that form of field labor,â said Sergey Ivanovitch.

âIâm awfully fond of it. I sometimes mow myself with the peasants, and
