âI hope you wonât be dull?â

âI hope not,â said Anna. âI got a box of books yesterday from
Gautierâs. No, I shanât be dull.â

âSheâs trying to take that tone, and so much the better,â he thought,
âor else it would be the same thing over and over again.â

